  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have just been born in a laboratory… and you’ve already been given a weapon. Now there’s only one objective: <strong>reach the other side of the tower</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175400/extras/6d599bba10accca342282085bc3487e7.poster.avif?t=1773836877\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175400/extras/6d599bba10accca342282085bc3487e7.webm?t=1773836877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175400/extras/6d599bba10accca342282085bc3487e7.mp4?t=1773836877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>IPO TOWER </strong>is a casual <strong><i>pixel art platformer</i></strong> with more than <strong>40 challenging levels</strong> that will test your precision, reflexes, and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow <strong>Ipo</strong>, the main character, as he faces traps, obstacles, and increasingly difficult challenges in his journey to escape the <i>tower</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 40 challenging levels featuring mechanics that make full use of your weapon</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging and intense boss fights</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A completely original and engaging soundtrack</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beautiful pixel art visuals</strong> (seriously!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175400/extras/60f21c3641fbc43d97b41cc039d1ba6b.poster.avif?t=1773836877\" width=1170 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175400/extras/60f21c3641fbc43d97b41cc039d1ba6b.webm?t=1773836877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175400/extras/60f21c3641fbc43d97b41cc039d1ba6b.mp4?t=1773836877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The coins (I forgot the coins)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                           Help Ipo<i><span class=\"bb_strike\">(please)</span></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          </p></li></ul>",
